(205, 50, 'content_description_5', 'I found great inspiration from several websites and essentially attempted to use those components in my own work. Websites that use colour and properly make use of transitions from one section to the next without losing the overall tone of the portfolio itself. If it works, it works; and this is what I considered as I moved forward with design decisions. There were several different websites that I found to use exciting and natural animations that are used in key areas that don\'t take away from the visitor\'s experience on the website itself.'),
(206, 50, '_content_description_5', 'field_641761ad3708c'),
(207, 50, 'content_description_6', 'I found great success in researching and preparing this web portfolio to summarize the main skills that I obtained in communicating with a headless CMS. I would like to build upon this portfolio and adjust it as I feel would better reflect my skills and capabilities; preferably showcasing my creativity through smooth animations and having the entire portfolio feel as though it flows smoothly within each section.'),
